summary: Completed comprehensive testing of H1B job listing website MVP. All core features working correctly including landing page, jobs browsing with filters, job details with wage level charts, companies listing, and company profiles. Backend APIs (19/19 tests passed) and frontend functionality fully operational.

design_issues.issue: Some company logos fail to load from clearbit.com (ERR_NAME_NOT_RESOLVED)
Chart width/height warnings in console but charts render correctly

passed_tests: Landing page loads with hero search, stats, and featured jobs
Jobs page displays all 20 seeded jobs with working filters
Search functionality works (returned 5 results for 'Software Engineer')
Wage level filter works (returned 3 results for Level 4)
Job detail page shows wage info, salary, requirements, and charts
Companies page shows all 8 companies with H1B approval stats
Company detail page shows company info and open positions
Save job button shows auth required message correctly
Apply button shows on job detail page
Backend API tests: 19/19 passed (100% success rate)
Frontend navigation and UI interactions working
Error handling for non-existent jobs/companies working
